  "content": {
    "raw": "<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"kkp\">\n<style>\n.kkp{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto}\n.kkp .kkp-lead{font-size:1.18rem;line-height:1.5;max-width:62ch;margin:0 0 .4rem}\n.kkp .kkp-lead.kkp-kicker{font-weight:700}\n.kkp .kkp-label{font-size:.74rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.14em;opacity:.55;margin:2rem 0 .85rem}\n.kkp .kkp-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(210px,1fr));gap:1rem}\n.kkp .kkp-card{display:block;border:1px solid rgba(150,150,160,.22);border-radius:11px;overflow:hidden;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;background:rgba(150,150,160,.05);transition:transform .15s ease,border-color .15s ease}\n.kkp .kkp-card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);border-color:#e5462e}\n.kkp .kkp-card img{width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/10;object-fit:cover;display:block}\n.kkp .kkp-txt{padding:.7rem .8rem .85rem}\n.kkp .kkp-title{font-weight:700;font-size:.96rem;line-height:1.25}\n.kkp .kkp-sub{font-size:.8rem;opacity:.68;margin-top:.28rem;line-height:1.35}\n.kkp .kkp-cta{margin-top:2.4rem;padding-top:1.1rem;border-top:1px solid rgba(150,150,160,.22);font-size:1.02rem}\n.kkp .kkp-cta a{color:#e5462e;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none}\n.kkp .kkp-cta a:hover{text-decoration:underline}\n</style>\n\n<p class=\"kkp-lead kkp-kicker\">I didn't set out to build a scene. I went looking for my people.</p>\n<p class=\"kkp-lead\">Artists, hackers, researchers, founders, policy folks. The ones already doing the work before the global conferences showed up. That search became the Vancouver AI community and the BC + AI ecosystem. You are the BC + AI ecosystem.</p>\n\n<div class=\"kkp-label\">Start here</div>\n<div class=\"kkp-grid\">\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2025/05/18/bc-ai-is-live-and-were-building-the-future-we-actually-want/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bc-ai-header.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"BC + AI Ecosystem\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">BC + AI is live</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Why we built Canada's first grassroots AI industry association.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2025/02/02/vancouver-ai-january-2025-recap-one-year-of-creative-rebellion-open-source-disruption/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/MASTER-Blog-header-1.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"One year of the Vancouver AI meetup\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">One year in</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">From 80 pioneers to a province-wide community.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2026/06/01/long-road-to-futureproof/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/vanai21-kris-jonny-stage.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"The Long Road to Futureproof\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">The Long Road to Futureproof</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">The festival dream the community finally made real.</div></div></a>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"kkp-label\">Meetup recaps</div>\n<div class=\"kkp-grid\">\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2025/05/11/vancouver-ai-meetup-16-where-tech-creativity-and-community-collide/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/MASTER-Youtube-Thumbs-Twitter-Header.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"Vancouver AI Meetup #16\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Meetup #16</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Tech, creativity, and community collide.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2025/03/02/vancouver-ai-the-community-building-bcs-ai-future-february-meetup-recap/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/VAI14-YouTube-Thumbnail.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"February meetup recap\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">February recap</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Building BC's AI future, one meetup at a time.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2024/09/01/august-vancouver-ai-community-meetup-recap-hackers-hustlers-heretics/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MASTER-Blog-header.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"August meetup recap\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Hackers, hustlers, heretics</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">The August recap.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2024/01/28/inside-the-innaugural-vancouver-ai-community-meetup/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/jim-dine-vancouver-biennale-kris-krug-december2024-8-scaled-e1706462715943.jpg?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"The first Vancouver AI meetup\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Where it started</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Inside the very first meetup.</div></div></a>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"kkp-label\">The bigger story</div>\n<div class=\"kkp-grid\">\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2025/04/19/vancouvers-ai-how-grassroots-innovation-is-reshaping-british-columbias-tech-future/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/bc-studies-ai-community.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"DIY AI in Vancouver\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">DIY AI in Vancouver</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">How grassroots innovation reshaped BC's tech future.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2025/02/16/bcs-ai-ecosystem-a-mycelial-network-of-creation/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kk-bc-ai.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"A mycelial network of creation\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">A mycelial network</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Fifteen months mapping the builders making AI on their own terms.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2024/06/19/blog-rise-of-the-vancouver-technopunks-hosting-the-web-summit-on-our-terms/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Copy-of-AI-Immortality-w-Guy-Kawasaki-1-1.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"Rise of the Vancouver technopunks\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Rise of the technopunks</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Hosting the Web Summit on our terms.</div></div></a>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"kkp-cta\">Browse the full <a href=\"https://kriskrug.co/category/vancouver-ai-ecosystem/\">Vancouver AI Ecosystem archive</a>, or <a href=\"https://kriskrug.co/speaking/\">bring this energy to your event</a>.</p>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n",
