ing AI on their own terms.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2024/06/19/blog-rise-of-the-vancouver-technopunks-hosting-the-web-summit-on-our-terms/\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Copy-of-AI-Immortality-w-Guy-Kawasaki-1-1.png?resize=640,400&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"Rise of the Vancouver technopunks\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Rise of the technopunks</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Hosting the Web Summit on our terms.</div></div></a>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"kkp-cta\">Browse the full <a href=\"https://kriskrug.co/category/vancouver-ai-ecosystem/\">Vancouver AI Ecosystem archive</a>, or <a href=\"https://kriskrug.co/speaking/\">bring this energy to your event</a>.</p>\n</div>\n\n",
